<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1436,2002,2028]" lastBlockId="9.[151,1437,152,476]" lastPageId="9" lastPageNumber="42" pageId="8" pageNumber="41">
Reported as a widespread 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[467,482,2002,2028]" pageId="8" pageNumber="41">“</emphasis>
Euro-Siberian species” by zur Strassen (
<number box="[965,1029,2002,2028]" pageId="8" pageNumber="41" value="2003.0">2003</number>
a), this species was recorded from wheat and barley in 
<collectingCountry box="[386,436,152,178]" name="Iran" pageId="9" pageNumber="42">Iran</collectingCountry>
, Golestan Province by 
<bibRefCitation author="Alavi" box="[705,855,152,178]" pageId="9" pageNumber="42" refString="Alavi, J. (2000) Faunistic study of Thysanoptera on wheat and barley in Golestan province. Proceedings of the 14 th Iranian Plant Protection Congress, Vol. I, Pests, p. 227." type="proceedings paper" year="2000">
Alavi (
<number box="[785,847,152,178]" pageId="9" pageNumber="42" value="2000.0">2000</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
and from Bojnourd by 
<bibRefCitation author="Alavi" box="[1127,1400,152,178]" pageId="9" pageNumber="42" refString="Alavi, J. &amp; Kamali, K. (2003) The fauna of Thysanoptera in Bojnourd region of Khorasan province, Iran. Thrips 2, 25 - 40." type="journal article" year="2003">
Alavi &amp; Kamali (
<number box="[1330,1391,152,178]" pageId="9" pageNumber="42" value="2003.0">2003</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
on 
<taxonomicName box="[151,365,189,214]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Cynodontidae" genus="Cynodon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Characiformes" pageId="9" pageNumber="42" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="dactylon">
